Most recent version: <b>1.4</b> &nbsp;


Selected version: <b>1.4</b> Added: <b>2 May 2019</b>
<br/>

<br/>

- Module name is now XMPP<br/>- Support stream feature negotiation for starttls, sasl (PLAIN only ATM), bind and session<br/>- Pike 8.0 support<br/>- More reliable I/O<br/>- Added connect callback<p/>
